```plantuml
@startuml Luizbrandt_users-crud-salesforce
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Client

rectangle "MuleSoft API" as MuleAPI #lightblue {
  rectangle "API Kit Router" as Router
  rectangle "Mule Flows" as Flows
}

rectangle "Salesforce" as Salesforce #lightyellow {
  rectangle "Custom_User__c Object" as CustomUser
}

' ========== Connections ==========
Client --> Router : HTTP Requests\n(Create/Read/Update/Delete)

' API Kit Router interactions
Router --> Flows : Route to CRUD operations\nbased on RAML spec

' Mule Flows interactions
Flows --> Salesforce : Interact with Salesforce\nCRUD on Custom_User__c

' Error Handling and Data Transformation
Flows --> Flows : Handle errors\nTransform data with DataWeave

@enduml
```